# Minimal CIF fixture for Z-estimation tests
# Calcite CaCO3 -- R-3c, trigonal carbonate, Z=6, formula_derived expected
data_CaCO3_calcite
_chemical_formula_sum 'C Ca O3'
_cell_formula_units_Z 6
_cell_length_a 4.9896
_cell_length_b 4.9896
_cell_length_c 17.061
_cell_angle_alpha 90.0
_cell_angle_beta 90.0
_cell_angle_gamma 120.0
_symmetry_space_group_name_H-M 'R -3 c'

loop_
